 id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qql1665702730534.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qql1665702730534.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qql1665702730534.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qql1665702730534\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      updblobspr\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether Uniface should use stored procedures when updating BLOB data (SC*)\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qql1665702730534__topic_d52640e1_d52641e1_d52642e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qql1665702730534__p_d52643e1_d52644e1_d52645e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS = updblobspr: on | off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qql1665702730534__section_ljs_s5h_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d560697e60\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qql1665702730534__p_d52649e1_d52650e1_d52651e1\">The option <code class=\"ph codeph\">updblobspr</code> works only if\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">segmented fields</code> (also known as the <code class=\"ph codeph\">blobs</code> option)\n            is set <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qql1665702730534__section_gtv_t5h_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d560697e81\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qql1665702730534__p_d52655e1_d52656e1_d52657e1\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">updblobspr</code> (‘Update BLOB field\n            with Stored Procedure’) is set <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>, then stored procedures will be used\n            to update the BLOB (SC*) fields.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohd1665702931867.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>segmented fields</a><p>Specify whether segmented fields will be stored to large object data types.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531382\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531382\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "updblobspr Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 updblobspr Specify whether Uniface should use stored procedures when updating BLOB data (SC*) USYS$MSS_PARAMS = updblobspr: on | off Use The option updblobspr works only if segmented fields (also known as the blobs option) is set on . Description If updblobspr (‘Update BLOB field with Stored Procedure’) is set on , then stored procedures will be used to update the BLOB (SC*) fields. Related Links segmented fields Specify whether segmented fields will be stored to large object data types. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}